programlisting.code:
Create Spacecraft sc Create Propagator prop Create EphemerisFile ephem ephem.Spacecraft = sc ephem.Filename = 'ephem.eph' ephem.FileFormat = 'Code-500' ephem.StepSize = 60 ephem.OutputFormat = 'PC'
BeginMissionSequence
Propagate prop(sc) {sc.ElapsedDays = 1}

listitem.para:
The deprecated fields
        Thruster.Element{1–3}
        have been removed. Use
        Thruster.ThrustDirection{1–3}
        instead. See the Thruster reference
        for details.
